Chiew-Lan Tai is a Professor at the Hong Kong University of Science & Technology. 
She received her B.Sc. and M.Sc. in Mathematics from the University of Malaya, M.Sc. in Computer and Information Sciences from the National University of Singapore, and D.Sc. in Information Science from the University of Tokyo.
Her research interests include geometric processing, computer graphics, human computer interaction, and computer vision. 

